{"tid":2517699,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 第74屆康城影展 Cannes 2021","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T15:16:16.000Z","uid":121740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47d670064b3201eacb200c188ac9692c86de712b","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resize-media.festival-cannes.com/fit-in/2560x1620/media_image/0001/74/f94788eb87ac41aa9f31f779bf48779b5eeac398.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresize-media.festival-cannes.com%2Ffit-in%2F2560x1620%2Fmedia_image%2F0001%2F74%2Ff94788eb87ac41aa9f31f779bf48779b5eeac398.jpeg&h=ab8903b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉行：2021年7月6日至17日（當地）<br />\n藝術總監：Thierry Fr&eacute;maux<br />\n評審團主席：Spike Lee（美國）<br />\n片單公佈：5月27日（Press Conference） <br />\n<br />\n歷屆討論區（70th to 73rd）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913136</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1113989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1113989</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/625468/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/625468/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/245359/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/245359/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.festival-cannes.com/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.festival-cannes.com%2Fzh%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=e1f1cc4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.festival-cannes.com/zh/</a> <br />\n<br />\n一同期待全球影壇年度盛事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da67d450002b6b1641be92e7fd2f3821da1da75","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"已確認入選主競賽單元（Official Selection） <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Paul Verhoeven《Benedetta》<br />\nLeos Carax《Annette》 </span><br />\n<br />\n繼早前公佈法國導演 Leos Carax 睽違九年首部英語電影《Annette》為康城揭開序幕的消息外，官方今日亦確認了名導Paul Verhoeven的《Benedetta》入選主競賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdWiNyR2Jpjx9kdEcFX6aFetLRPBtn3NzyvyeB2kLW81M?filename=UAoYv4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAoYv4O.jpg&h=b70ffd9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由 Virginie Efira 主演、改編自 Judith C. Brown 的著作，講述17世紀意大利修女 Benedetta Carlini 經常產生幻覺，及後更與另一名修女發生關係的經過。 <br />\n<br />\n先行預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n-31QJXV3iA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn-31QJXV3iA&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=ef8d58cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n-31QJXV3iA</a>"},{"pid":"ec32c508405f3a84d6451bbc533ab3a07448b0ac","tid":2517699,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇報導話PTA想去康城，但發行商傾向去威尼斯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldofreel.com/blog/2021/5/ytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldofreel.com%2Fblog%2F2021%2F5%2Fytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=f1a18cf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldofreel.com/blog/2021/5/ytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti</a>"},{"pid":"5a3f8b4d995c8a97e3734a766e1b393197f649a8","tid":2517699,"uid":264685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f2251435695cef3c005c04b708c9d6b3d8af6f","tid":2517699,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://25.media.tumblr.com/548f3ef3156fa0960ce8e07942d1ad1c/tumblr_mhidmoPHUE1rot0kgo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F25.media.tumblr.com%2F548f3ef3156fa0960ce8e07942d1ad1c%2Ftumblr_mhidmoPHUE1rot0kgo1_500.gif&h=67f8130e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"494079472c1396097ae529276719aa09ad13639a","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"那些很有可能在康城亮相的有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMia Hansen-L&oslash;ve《Bergman Island》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTQkbKvGwxwhXUh6XbzoFakLTpgeHefERxASQ5hgHaxLC?filename=gR1vnT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgR1vnT1.jpg&h=e594868a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據法國發行Les Films du Losange 的排片時間表，該片將於7月14日（國慶日）公映，恰好也正值影展舉行期間，料採取「康城+全法院線」同步上映。<br />\n<br />\n該片講述一對從事電影製作產業的美國夫妻（情侶）在夏季的時候來到了一座小島上為他們的下一部電影尋求劇本的靈感，而這座島也就是 Ingmar Bergman 曾經常居且永眠的「法羅島」。<br />\n<br />\n然而在隨著夏季以及他們所創作的電影劇本的發展，在於島上景色那現實與虛構之間的界線卻也逐漸的模糊&hellip;"}]}